# Optional overrides for the e2e suite. Copy to tests/e2e/.env if needed.
#
# By default the suite expects .dev.vars (project root) to contain:
#   ADMIN_USERNAME=admin
#   ADMIN_PASSWORD_HASH=<hash of "e2e-test-pass">
#   AUTH_SECRET=<any long random string>
#
# Generate the hash once with:
#   pnpm hash e2e-test-pass
# Then paste into .dev.vars.
#
# Override the credentials the tests use here if your local .dev.vars
# uses a different password (note: this file is NOT auto-loaded by
# Playwright — set the variables in your shell before running pnpm test:e2e).
#
# E2E_USERNAME=admin
# E2E_PASSWORD=e2e-test-pass
# E2E_PORT=3000
